    "summary": "A complete personal knowledge management system combining tools, processes, and practices.",
    "explanation": "A PKM System (PKMS) is a complete personal knowledge management system that combines tools, processes, and practices for managing personal information and knowledge. Elements include: capture mechanisms, organization structure, note types, linking practices, review processes, and output workflows. The right way to think about a PKM system is as an integral part of everything you do. It should be one you can actually trust with important memories, ideas, insights, information, knowledge, and wisdom.",
